songs.comment_text: I am 64 years old and I got so emotional watching this. Thinking back to my wild days and the fun I had in my 20's. Now I am nursing my bad back and basically watching myself grow old. I wouldn't change anything and even this stage of my life is okay even though things are different. Thank you Miley for writing a beautiful song that even a 64 year old can relate to.
